@casebenton add this chunk of CSS [here](https://github.com/mozilla/normandy/blob/master/normandy/control/static/control/admin/sass/control.scss#L128) and just check that it looks ok. (Should right-align the error message, make it a little smaller and red.)

```
  .validation-error {
    color: $red;
    float: right;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }
```

